Package com.intexsoft.cli.model

Interface Summary
Library The interfase defining methods characteristic for the library classes.
 

Class Summary
AbstractLibrary The abstract class for library classes.
Book The class defining a book in a library.
CLIModel The class represent a model of the Central Libraries Index (CLI).
CSVLibrary Implementation of the AbstractLibrary class.
TEXTLibrary Implementation the abstract class AbstractLibrary.
 

Exception Summary
DeleteFileException The exception throws when a program can't delete a file.
FindBookException The exception throws when occured an error when finding a book.
FindBookInCSVLibException The exception throws when occured an error when finding a book in the CSV-library.
FindBookInTEXTLibException The exception throws when occured an error when finding a book in the TEXT-library.
OrderBookException The exception throws when occured an error when ordering a book.
OrderBookInCSVLibException The exception throws when occured an error when ordering a book in the CSV-library.
OrderBookInTEXTLibException The exception throws when occured an error when ordering a book in the TEXT-library.
RenameTmpFileException The exception throws when a program can't rename temporality file.
ReturnBookException The exception throws when occured an error when returning a book.
ReturnBookInCSVLibException The exception throws when occured an error when returning a book in the CSV-library.
ReturnBookInTEXTLibException The exception throws when occured an error when returning a book in the TEXT-library.
